msgid ""
msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "And what about the father?\r\nWho's the father of this child!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "We don't know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "You don't <font_kind=yakuza_italic>know</font_kind>?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "There was nothing on her person that\r\nwould have helped us identify him."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Her phone was broken in the accident,\r\nbut we're trying to extract its data."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "Beyond that, we aren't even sure\r\nwhen Haruka arrived in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "We'll have to ask her once she wakes up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "And she's definitely going to wake up?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "We can't promise that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "My apologies, but I don't want to give\r\nyou any false hope here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "The doctors are doing everything in\r\ntheir power. All we can do is pray."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "Senpai, I should get going. There's still\r\nwork to be done at the crime scene."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Hold on a minute.\r\nHonjo-san, wasn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Where did her accident happen?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Why does it matter? Going there\r\nyourself won't change the situation."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "We're already pursuing the culprit.\r\nA washed-up yakuza should stay out of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Hey, Honjo.\r\nWatch your mouth."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "He can say whatever he wants.\r\nI'm not going to just stand here and wait."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Haruka should have been in Okinawa,\r\nbut she ended up in an accident here instead."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "I don't understand.\r\nWho was the bastard driving that car?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "And more importantly, was this\r\nreally just a simple accident?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "But Haruka..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Do you mean someone may have tried to\r\nkill her? Maybe to get revenge on you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "It's possible.\r\nAnd there would be no forgiveness."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Wait. All right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "The accident took place near Senryo Avenue.\r\nI can take you there if you'd like."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "That okay by you, Date-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Yeah, if you don't mind. Thanks."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "We're here. Haruka Sawamura was here\r\nwith her child just a few hours ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "At that point, she was struck\r\nfrom behind by a black sedan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "The car flew out of that parking garage,\r\ntaking out the gate in the process."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "In the car was a lone man."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Some gangbanger in his twenties.\r\nHe fled immediately after hitting them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "A gang..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Remember, the Tojo Clan and the\r\ntriads are in an all-out war."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "It's possible our culprit was trying to\r\nescape from a related incident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Which would be why he lost\r\ncontrol of the car..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "If you're right, which side was he on?\r\nTojo Clan or the triads?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "Not necessarily either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "It's not like those are the only\r\nactive syndicates in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Let me back up a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "Three months ago, a Chinese immigrant\r\nwas murdered. He was Saio Triad."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "And not only was he a ranking officer,\r\nbut he was the boss's only son, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "In other words, he stood to inherit\r\nthe entire triad. His name was Jimmy Lo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "Tensions really escalated after his death."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "The Tojo's sixth chairman was arrested,\r\nand the conflict sparked up all over again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "And the Tojo Clan?\r\nDid they kill Jimmy Lo?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "We're still not sure ourselves.\r\nThe Saio seem to believe so, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "They've started scouring the city for any\r\nTojo yakuza they can get their hands on."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "To retaliate, the Tojo Clan has been driving\r\nthe Chinese out, even civilians. It's a mess."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "To top it off, other groups are moving into\r\nKamurocho to take advantage of the chaos."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "There's no way that the Tojo and the Saio\r\nare the only ones involved in this by now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "It wouldn't surprise me if the guy who\r\nhit Haruka was from a third party."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "Oh, and I should mention..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "You have a history with one of the\r\norganizations that's crept into Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "A Korean gang, the Jingweon Mafia."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "The Jingweon..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Both times they expanded into Kamurocho,\r\nthey were obliterated by the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "The first time was over thirty years ago,\r\nand the second was just a decade back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "I'm told you played a large role in\r\ncrushing them with the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "That was ages ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "It may be to you, but they remember\r\ntheir grudges, both with you and the Tojo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "If you plan on staying in Kamurocho,\r\nI suggest you watch your back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "(What was Haruka doing here?\r\nAnd with her child, no less...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "(Not many cars come down this street.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "(I bet there are still some clues\r\nrelated to the incident around here.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "(Apparently the culprit's car came\r\nspeeding out of that parking garage.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "(The gate got torn down in the process.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "(He must have already been going\r\npretty fast by the time he reached it...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "(Tire tracks?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "(The car was probably swerving down\r\nthe road as he tried to regain control.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "(But why was the driver being so reckless?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "(Was he really just panicked?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "(Blood spatters... This must be where\r\nHaruka was hit by the car.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "That's where Haruka Sawamura was\r\nwalking when the car came."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "She tried to get out of the way once\r\nshe noticed, but there was no escape."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "All she could do was wrap herself\r\naround the child to keep him safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "Damn..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "Look around you, though.\r\nThere are skid marks all over the road."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "After he hit Haruka, the driver tried to\r\nstop, but then he second-guessed it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "He must have been in quite a hurry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "He didn't even stop to check if the\r\nyoung woman he'd hit was alive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "So? What are you getting at?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Let's think about this. Assuming the driver\r\nwent after Haruka to get revenge on you...\r\n"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "...Wouldn't he need to check whether\r\nor not she was still alive afterward?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "But in this case, the culprit didn't do\r\nthat. There can only be one reason."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "Your history as a yakuza had nothing\r\nto do with why she was hit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "It was just an unfortunate accident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96||||4"
msgid "She was in the wrong place at the wrong\r\ntime. You should put your mind at ease."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "97||||4"
msgid "But that punk driver...\r\nHe's still out there, isn't he?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "98||||4"
msgid "Is it really that easy for a common thug\r\nto escape from the law these days?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "99||||4"
msgid "The police are making a concerted effort\r\nto find him. It's too early to say \"escaped.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "101||||4"
msgid "By the way, perhaps you\r\nhaven't noticed..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "102||||4"
msgid "...But you're being watched."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "103||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "104||||4"
msgid "That guy in the hat?\r\nHow long has he been there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "105||||4"
msgid "I only just spotted him, but he's\r\ncertainly trying to record you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "106||||4"
msgid "The guy on the motorcycle?\r\nHow long has he been there?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "107||||4"
msgid "What'll you do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108||||4"
msgid "Is he keeping tabs on me?\r\nOr is he here to see the crime scene?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "109||||4"
msgid "Just wanna have a chat. If he's interested\r\nin me, I should give him a personal intro."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "111||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'm there now.\r\nEverything's going smoothly."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "112||||4"
msgid "Hey."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "113||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "114||||4"
msgid "What are you up to here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "115||||4"
msgid "...Shit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "116||||4"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "117||||4"
msgid "Hey, I sait wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "118||||4"
msgid "Damn, where'd he go!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "119||||4"
msgid "Stop!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120||||4"
msgid "Hey, come back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "121||||4"
msgid "Dammit!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "122||||4"
msgid "Huh!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "124||||4"
msgid "Give up!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "126||||4"
msgid "Who the hell are you?\r\nAnd why were you spying on me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "127||||4"
msgid "I-I wasn't spying on you, I swear!\r\nI was protecting you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "128||||4"
msgid "Fourth Chairman."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "129||||4"
msgid "Wait, you're Tojo Clan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "130||||4"
msgid "Yes. I'm from the Someya Family,\r\none of the Tojo Clan subsidiaries."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "131||||4"
msgid "Someya?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132||||4"
msgid "Please forgive me, Fourth Chairman!\r\nMy boss ordered me to!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "133||||4"
msgid "He wanted me to stay in the shadows\r\nto make sure you stay safe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "134||||4"
msgid "But I just got to Kamurocho today, and no\r\none from the Tojo Clan knew I was coming."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "135||||4"
msgid "This doesn't make any sense.\r\nHow did they know I'd be here?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "136||||4"
msgid "I'm not really sure myself.\r\nI was just following orders, sir."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "137||||4"
msgid "He said if I waited by that alley,\r\nyou would show up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "138||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "139||||4"
msgid "He also told me someone very\r\nimportant to you was in an accident."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "141||||4"
msgid "My boss seems to know a lot about you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "142||||4"
msgid "So he does. And where exactly is\r\nthis boss of yours now?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144||||4"
msgid "Where can I meet with the\r\npatriarch of the Someya Family?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "145||||4"
msgid "I have contacts who can\r\ntell me if you won't."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "146||||4"
msgid "But I'd rather save us both some time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "147||||4"
msgid "If you insist. My boss..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "148||||4"
msgid "He's at Tojo Headquarters. He said he had\r\na meeting with Acting Chairman Sugai."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "149||||4"
msgid "Tojo Headquarters... Damn it, I never\r\nwanted to set foot in there again."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "150||||4"
msgid "Um, is something wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "151||||4"
msgid "I just spent three years in prison to\r\nwash off the stench of the Tojo Clan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "152||||4"
msgid "I've only been out for a few days,\r\nand I'm already getting pulled back in..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "153||||4"
msgid "(What does the Someya Family patriarch\r\nknow about me and Haruka's accident?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "154||||4"
msgid "(Looks like my answers are at Tojo Clan\r\nHeadquarters. I should find a taxi...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "155||||4"
msgid "(After all that, I still don't have any leads.\r\nCan I really count on the police to find this guy?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156||||4"
msgid "(Maybe I should head back to New Serena\r\nin case there's been any updates...)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "157||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "158||||4"
msgid "I heard from Date-san earlier.\r\nHe said Haruka-chan was in an accident?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "159||||4"
msgid "Yeah. As we speak, she's in\r\ncritical condition in the ICU."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "160||||4"
msgid "They haven't found the guy who did it yet,\r\neither."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "161||||4"
msgid "I'm trying to find out what I can on my own, too.\r\nNo luck yet, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "162||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san.\r\nYou have a smartphone, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "163||||4"
msgid "I do."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "164||||4"
msgid "Can I see it for a sec?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "165||||4"
msgid "There, that should do it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "166||||4"
msgid "Hm? What did you do?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "167||||4"
msgid "I installed an app that serves as a\r\nsort of bulletin board for Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure, but you might be\r\nable to find some info there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "169||||4"
msgid "Thanks for that, Mama.\r\nI'll look at it later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "170||||4"
msgid "Date-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "171||||4"
msgid "Yeah, it's me. Akiyama's here\r\nwith me at the hospital now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "172||||4"
msgid "You should come back if you can.\r\nI need to head out for a bit."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "173||||4"
msgid "Okay, I'll be right there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "174||||4"
msgid "See you later, then."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "175||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "176||||4"
msgid "Akiyama. Hm?\r\nWhat's this? You got cleaned up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "177||||4"
msgid "Yeah, well... I kept getting turned\r\naway at the door in those rags."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "178||||4"
msgid "Date-san told me everything, though.\r\nHaruka-chan's still in the ICU."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "179||||4"
msgid "She's still unresponsive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180||||4"
msgid "I see."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "181||||4"
msgid "One more thing, Kiryu-san.\r\nIt's about Haruka-chan's kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "182||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "183||||4"
msgid "There's a guy here from Child Services.\r\nSays he wants to talk to you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "184||||4"
msgid "You're Haruka Sawamura's associate, yes?\r\nI'm Nojiri from Child Protection Services."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "185||||4"
msgid "I received a call earlier today asking me\r\nto retrieve her child from this hospital."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "186||||4"
msgid "What?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "187||||4"
msgid "As Sawamura-san has no living relatives,\r\nwe will be taking custody of the child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "188||||4"
msgid "This is just standard procedure in these\r\ncases. Sorry, but if you'll excuse me..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "189||||4"
msgid "Is Haruka's son going to\r\nend up in an orphanage?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "190||||4"
msgid "Yes, though considering he's not even a\r\nyear old, he'll go to a nursery first."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "191||||4"
msgid "Regardless, he must be taken in until\r\nSawamura-san can fully recover."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192||||4"
msgid "Hold on a second. I'm Haruka Sawamura's\r\nguardian. The name's Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "193||||4"
msgid "I can take responsibility for her child.\r\nYou guys don't need to get involved."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "194||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "195||||4"
msgid "You claim to be her guardian,\r\nyet you're not related to her?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "196||||4"
msgid "Therefore you're a self-proclaimed guardian\r\nwho has no legal claim to the child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "197||||4"
msgid "Imagine. What if you were only saying\r\nthat to harvest the baby's organs or something?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "198||||4"
msgid "Excuse me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "199||||4"
msgid "The hell?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "200||||4"
msgid "Sorry, I suppose that was\r\na bit of an exaggeration."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "201||||4"
msgid "But if we did hand the child over to you,\r\nthe liability would fall directly on us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "202||||4"
msgid "Nowadays when a parent beats their child\r\nto death, the public blames our agency."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "203||||4"
msgid "People simply choose to ignore the fact\r\nthat we're understaffed and overworked."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204||||4"
msgid "If anything were to happen to the child\r\nunder your care, we would take the fall."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "205||||4"
msgid "Please try to understand my position."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "206||||4"
msgid "Look. It's Nojiri-san, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "207||||4"
msgid "Is everyone in Child Protection Services\r\na bastard like you? Couldn't be, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "208||||4"
msgid "Pardon?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "209||||4"
msgid "You don't even care about the kids.\r\nAll that matters to you is your position."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "211||||4"
msgid "Haruka and I were raised in an orphanage."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "212||||4"
msgid "If you grew up with parents watching over you,\r\nyou'll never know how painful that can be."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "214||||4"
msgid "So listen up. I won't let you send a kid\r\nwho can't even talk to a place like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "215||||4"
msgid "Haruka would say the same\r\nthing if she were conscious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "216||||4"
msgid "Talk all you want,\r\nbut it doesn't change facts."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "217||||4"
msgid "If you're not a direct relative, you have\r\nno sway over what happens to this child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "218||||4"
msgid "The police never should have called you\r\nhere. You're just interfering."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "219||||4"
msgid "Now then, I need to go speak to\r\na hospital representative."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "221||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san, where you going?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "222||||4"
msgid "I'm not letting them take\r\nHaruka's child away from her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "223||||4"
msgid "What? Hey, Kiryu-san!\r\nChill out a minute!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "224||||4"
msgid "Man... I just can't bring myself\r\nto fight you for real."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "225||||4"
msgid "Got my ass kicked for nothing."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "226||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry, Akiyama."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "227||||4"
msgid "Is taking the kid really the only way?\r\nWe're all kinda screwed, you know."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "228||||4"
msgid "I know I act before I think sometimes.\r\nCall it a bad habit of mine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "229||||4"
msgid "Such a you answer. Guess that's why\r\nyou're the one and only Kazuma Kiryu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "230||||4"
msgid "There, there. That's it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "231||||4"
msgid "Don't drop him.\r\nEasy now, be gentle."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "232||||4"
msgid "Oh, please."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "234||||4"
msgid "Remember Nojiri\r\nfrom Child Protective Services?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "235||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "236||||4"
msgid "I convinced him to let you take the kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "237||||4"
msgid "Told him I'd take the fall for anything\r\nthat might happen under your care."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "238||||4"
msgid "You did that for me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "239||||4"
msgid "Want to know what he said next?\r\n\"Take him for all I care.\""
msgstr ""

msgctxt "240||||4"
msgid "Said he'd forget about the whole\r\nhospital incident with you, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "241||||4"
msgid "Bastard doesn't give a damn about\r\nkids long as they're not on his list."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "243||||4"
msgid "Hopefully guys like him are\r\nan exception to the rule."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "244||||4"
msgid "He's probably got a lot on his plate\r\nwith Child Services so understaffed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "245||||4"
msgid "Apparently he's requested a transfer.\r\nThey oughta grant it, for the kids' sake."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "246||||4"
msgid "Not to mention the pride of everyone\r\nwith any pride working at the agency."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "247||||4"
msgid "I'm sorry for all of this, Date-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "248||||4"
msgid "It's nothing. I was pretty worried about\r\nHaruka's kid getting taken away myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "249||||4"
msgid "He reminds me of Saya at that age."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "250||||4"
msgid "She's all grown up now, though.\r\nIn control of her own life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "251||||4"
msgid "Saya... Has it really been ten years since\r\nshe got caught up in that host scam?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "252||||4"
msgid "Yeah. Hands down one of the\r\ndarkest moments of my life."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "253||||4"
msgid "If you hadn't been there to help us out,\r\nboth Saya and I would be goners."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "254||||4"
msgid "You know Kiryu, it feels like I still\r\nhaven't thanked you for all you did for us."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "255||||4"
msgid "Then drinks are on you tonight, Date-san?\r\nThat would make a 10-year-old debt even."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "256||||4"
msgid "Hell no, it wouldn't even come close."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "257||||4"
msgid "This is kinda hard to say,\r\nbut I've got some news for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "259||||4"
msgid "About Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "260||||4"
msgid "So it seems.\r\nAfter that..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "261||||4"
msgid "...She decided to come back to Kamurocho\r\nand got in the accident with her son today."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "262||||4"
msgid "I can't say for sure, but it's likely Haruka\r\nspent those years in Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "264||||4"
msgid "Haruto's father is in Hiroshima then?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "265||||4"
msgid "He may know what Haruka's been up to.\r\nAnd why she was in Kamurocho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "266||||4"
msgid "I bet he could tell you everything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "268||||4"
msgid "So... What's next, Kiryu?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "269||||4"
msgid "Let's just say I have a lot of questions\r\nfor this guy when I find him. But first..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "270||||4"
msgid "...I'll teach him a lesson about being\r\naround for the birth of a child."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "271||||4"
msgid "He's going to learn how a real father\r\ntakes care of his children."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "273||||4"
msgid "I'll leave for Hiroshima tomorrow,\r\nwith Haruto."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "274||||4"
msgid "I'm not sure that's the best idea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "275||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "276||||4"
msgid "Hiroshima is home to the Yomei Alliance."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "277||||4"
msgid "The Yomei Alliance..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "278||||4"
msgid "After the Omi and the Tojo, they're\r\neasily the third strongest clan in Japan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "279||||4"
msgid "They've never allied before, which keeps\r\nthem neutral. They're not hostile, either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "280||||4"
msgid "That might sound downright agreeable,\r\nbut that doesn't mean you want to test them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "281||||4"
msgid "They don't exactly take kindly to intruders."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "282||||4"
msgid "The Omi Alliance tried, but not even\r\nthey could push into Yomei turf."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "283||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I was always told to stay out of\r\nHiroshima. Nobody ever said why, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "284||||4"
msgid "The Yomei Alliance practically\r\noperates like a medieval shogunate."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "285||||4"
msgid "Instead of focusing on expansion,\r\nChairman Kurusu fortified his own turf."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "286||||4"
msgid "Takeru Kurusu..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "287||||4"
msgid "I'm sure the name rings a few bells,\r\nconsidering the world you left behind."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "288||||4"
msgid "He was a famous gambler after the war,\r\nand some would call him a living legend."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "289||||4"
msgid "Right, but... I never heard of anyone who\r\nactually met him during my Tojo days."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "290||||4"
msgid "Seeing as the Yomei cut off communication to\r\nthe outside, we have almost nothing on them."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "291||||4"
msgid "Even the police haven't heard the name\r\nTakeru Kurusu since the mid 70s."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "292||||4"
msgid "So what you're telling me is that you\r\nguys don't know if he's even still alive?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "293||||4"
msgid "If he is, he'd be pushing 100 by now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "294||||4"
msgid "Hardly likely a guy with one foot in the\r\ngrave could keep a whole clan in check, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "295||||4"
msgid "Well according to a rumor,\r\nTakeru Kurusu actually died years ago."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "296||||4"
msgid "In his place, a captain named Koshimizu has\r\nbeen pulling the strings behind the scenes."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "297||||4"
msgid "Long story short, not even the cops can say\r\nwhat's going on in the shadows of Hiroshima."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "298||||4"
msgid "Exactly. And that's why you of\r\nall people should steer clear."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "299||||4"
msgid "One wrong move, and you could spark\r\na war between the Tojo and the Yomei."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "300||||4"
msgid "I'm just a civilian now.\r\nI don't have that kind of influence anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "301||||4"
msgid "Yeah, well, that's what I figured\r\nyou'd say anyway."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "302||||4"
msgid "Date-san. While I'm away from Tokyo,\r\nI need you to watch over Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "303||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll make sure she's okay.\r\nAkiyama would probably pitch in too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "304||||4"
msgid "I have to say, Haruka's kid\r\nturned out pretty damn cute."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "305||||4"
msgid "She probably knows better than anyone\r\nthat this is no time to be unconscious."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "307||||4"
msgid "I know Haruka's going to wake up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "308||||4"
msgid "And when she does, Kiryu, you better\r\nhave Haruto's father here to see it happen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "309||||4"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

